    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Play the demo version of “Kano. Stone Islands”, which includes a linear section demonstrating the starting location from the main game.</strong>  <br>  <br><u>In the demo version, you will have to:</u> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 1. Explore 2 levels with their own features. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 2. Solve puzzles. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 3. Fight with NPCs. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 4. Fight with the boss. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 5. Enjoy the atmosphere and beauty of the game world. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3279850/extras/31070b1e49eb6197325888b6f6644370.avif?t=1757994040\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3279850/extras_big/31070b1e49eb6197325888b6f6644370.avif?t=1757994040 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><u>Explore, fight and learn the mysterious plot.</u> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><u>Play the demo version and discover the beginning of an amazing journey!</u> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Thank you for visiting, I hope for your feedback.</strong> </p>",
